'''琥珀堡'''（{{lang-hi|'''आमेर क़िला'''}}，'''Amer Fort'''）位于印度[[拉贾斯坦邦|拉贾斯坦邦]][[斋浦尔|斋浦尔]]以北11公里的山丘上<ref name="Publishing2008">{{cite book|author=Outlook Publishing|title=Outlook|url=http://books.google.com/books?id=PTEEAAAAMBAJ&pg=PA39|accessdate=18 April 2011|date=1 December 2008|publisher=Outlook Publishing|pages=39–|archive-date=2020-05-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200505233212/https://books.google.com/books?id=PTEEAAAAMBAJ&pg=PA39|dead-url=no}}</ref>，是斋浦尔地区的主要名胜<ref name="Mancini2009">{{cite book|last=Mancini|first=Marc|title=Selling Destinations: Geography for the Travel Professional|url=http://books.google.com/books?id=Kp6ceVRUg8UC&pg=PA539|accessdate=19 April 2011|date=1 February 2009|publisher=Cengage Learning|isbn=978-1-4283-2142-7|page=539|archive-date=2019-12-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191215170145/https://books.google.com/books?id=Kp6ceVRUg8UC&pg=PA539|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="Abram2003">{{cite book|last=Abram|first=David|title=Rough guide to India|url=http://books.google.com/books?id=kAMik_6LbwUC&pg=PA161|accessdate=19 April 2011|date=15 December 2003|publisher=Rough Guides|isbn=978-1-84353-089-3|page=161|archive-date=2021-04-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210418145043/https://books.google.com/books?id=kAMik_6LbwUC&pg=PA161|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

琥珀堡用红色[[砂岩|砂岩]]和[[大理石|大理石]]建造。2007年，琥珀堡有140万访客，平均每天5000人<ref name="Publishing2008"/>。2013年，琥珀堡作为[[拉贾斯坦邦的山地要塞|拉贾斯坦邦的山地要塞]]的一部分，被列为[[世界遗产|世界遗产]]<ref>{{cite news|last1=Singh|first1=Mahim Pratap|title=Unesco declares 6 Rajasthan forts World Heritage Sites|url=http://www.thehindu.com/news/national/other-states/unesco-declares-6-rajasthan-forts-world-heritage-sites/article4838107.ece|accessdate=1 April 2015|publisher=[[The_Hindu|The Hindu]]|date=22 June 2013|archive-date=2018-04-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180405214409/http://www.thehindu.com/news/national/other-states/unesco-declares-6-rajasthan-forts-world-heritage-sites/article4838107.ece|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

